    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HUNT ME》是一款 1-4 人合作的恐怖生存游戏。收集仪式所需的材料，削弱威胁并将其驱逐。小心，你也是猎物！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/0053c1c4c2f4a2f29ca566e7625d84fb.poster.avif?t=1772211716\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/0053c1c4c2f4a2f29ca566e7625d84fb.webm?t=1772211716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/0053c1c4c2f4a2f29ca566e7625d84fb.mp4?t=1772211716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 易于掌握的游戏玩法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 利用猎人的视觉瞄准威胁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 绕着它移动，或用红外光与它对峙。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 收集仪式所需的材料。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 驱逐它！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/195b86822d501558d744c9611a1934e6.poster.avif?t=1772211716\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/195b86822d501558d744c9611a1934e6.webm?t=1772211716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/195b86822d501558d744c9611a1934e6.mp4?t=1772211716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可玩性</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仪式物品、生物、陷阱、安全点和骨头的位置都是随机生成的。人工智能的行为会受到玩家的行动和位置的影响--它们是不可预测的！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/8c1e9d0fad0380043518900ad3d98631.poster.avif?t=1772211716\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/8c1e9d0fad0380043518900ad3d98631.webm?t=1772211716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/8c1e9d0fad0380043518900ad3d98631.mp4?t=1772211716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >难度</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏共有 6 个难度级别和 100% 自定义模式。您可以按照自己的节奏探索游戏。最高难度需要策略、反应能力和对环境的掌控。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1 至 4 人合作模式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在多人模式中以团队形式进行狩猎。但别忘了，你也是猎物！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >单人游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HUNT ME 可以单人玩。您需要更复杂的策略。没有犯错的余地！</p>",
